The Horne Section TV Show series 2 - home of the best leg make up in the business 🎬

🇨🇦❤️
What a month - Watching baseball in Vancouver and cycling Stanley Park in torrential rain - Driving a 30ft RV to the Rockies via Zip lines in Whistler, night kayaking in Clearwater, then cycling in Jasper, paddling near Banff, massive steaks in Calgary and chilling on the beach in Tofino on Vancouver Island. Before a magical week spotting whales and bears, canyoning, canoeing and climbing, horse riding, biking, hiking and paddle boarding at Clayoquot ❤️ 
Early alarm set for next week!! ⏰
